<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Shelby Docs</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      color: #38bdf8;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #334155;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      color: #22c55e;
    }

    .box {
      background: #1e293b;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    code {
      display: block;
      background: #020617;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #38bdf8;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <h1>🚀 Shelby Quickstart Guide</h1>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>📋 System Requirements</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Node v22+</li>
      <li>Linux / MacOS</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>📦 Installation</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Fork repository</li>
      <li>Clone repo</li>
    </ol>

    <code>
git clone https://github.com/your-repo.git
cd your-repo
    </code>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>⚡ Run Project</h2>

    <code>
npm install
npm start
    </code>
  </div>

  <div class="box">
    <h2>🌐 Status</h2>
    <p>🚧 Public Beta Coming Soon</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
